description: Fully autonomous modular delivery constraints
globs: ["**/*"]
alwaysApply: true
---
- Never ask the user questions. If blocked, write a clear entry to ai/AUTOPILOT_LOG.md and stop.
- Do NOT modify:
  - .github/workflows/**
  - .cursor/rules/**
- Prefer small, vertically complete changes:
  spec -> contract -> code -> tests -> docs -> (green) pnpm test
- Every new feature must ship with tests.
